          <h3 class="font-bold text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-3 text-lg">Transition Moments</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark text-sm mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span>•</span><span><strong class="text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">Between tasks:</strong> Even 30 seconds of conscious walking clears your mind. Arrive at the new task fresh.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span>•</span><span><strong class="text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">After difficult conversations:</strong> Take 5 minutes to walk mindfully. Return to equilibrium.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span>•</span><span><strong class="text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">Before important events:</strong> Walk kinhin for 10 minutes. Arrive centered and present.</span></li>
