        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-[1.5rem] font-medium lg:text-3xl lg:font-medium text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-6">One Step at a Time</h2>

          <p class="text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark mb-4">
            In our hurried world, kinhin offers something radical: permission to slow down, to be fully present, to make each step count. You don't need to walk far—even ten steps with full awareness is complete in itself.
